"SQL Query": SELECT `nodes`.`NODENAME`, SUM(`dedup_stats`.`UNIQUE_BYTES`/1000000) FROM `dedup_stats` INNER JOIN `nodes` ON `dedup_stats`.`NODEID` = `nodes`.`NODEID` WHERE UNIQUE_BYTES NOT LIKE '' GROUP BY `dedup_stats`.`NODEID` ORDER BY `dedup_stats`.`NODEID`
SELECT STGPOOL_NAME, TOTAL_SPACE_MB FROM `stgpools` WHERE TOTAL_SPACE_MB > 0 GROUP BY STGPOOL_NAME ORDER BY `stgpools`.`STGPOOL_NAME`
SELECT NODEID, COUNT(NODEID) FROM `replicated_objects` GROUP BY NODEID
SELECT VOLID, SEGSIZE/1000000 from `af_segments` WHERE SEGSIZE NOT LIKE '' GROUP BY VOLID ORDER BY `af_segments`.`VOLID`
SELECT `nodes`.`NODENAME`, COUNT(`replicated_objects`.`NODEID`) FROM `replicated_objects` INNER JOIN `nodes` ON `replicated_objects`.`NODEID` = `nodes`.`NODEID` GROUP BY `replicated_objects`.`NODEID`
SELECT `STGPOOL_NAME` , SUM(`OBJECT_COUNT`) FROM `containers` WHERE OBJECT_COUNT NOT LIKE '' GROUP BY `STGPOOL_NAME`
SELECT `POOLID` , SUM(`REFCOUNT`) FROM `sd_chunk_locations` WHERE `REFCOUNT` NOT LIKE '' GROUP BY `POOLID`
SELECT `CHUNKID` , SUM(`REFCOUNT`) FROM `sd_chunk_locations` WHERE `REFCOUNT` NOT LIKE '' GROUP BY `CHUNKID`
SELECT `CNTRID` , SUM(`REFCOUNT`) FROM `sd_chunk_locations` WHERE `REFCOUNT` NOT LIKE '' GROUP BY `CNTRID`
SELECT POOLID, FILESIZE, MAXSIZE FROM `sd_containers` GROUP BY POOLID
